{"about_the_game":"Wildwood is a city building strategy game that is all about expansion. Start from nothing. As you gather resources and progress through the Tech Tree you will unlock new technologies that will help you survive. To reach more valuable resources you will need to expand. Deploy a logistics network of Trains and Wagons to connect your settlement together. As you continue to gather, build, expand, and connect you will be able to turn your surviving settlement into a thriving town.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303470/extras/Build.gif?t=1691646336\" /><br>Help your citizens thrive by building homes and workplaces for them. As you progress through the tech tree you will unlock new items and buildings that will help you in your quest to expand your settlement<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303470/extras/Explore.gif?t=1691646336\" /><br>The procedurally generated world of Wildwood is infinite. Explore new areas and take advantage of the resources available there. Expand your settlement as far as your heart desires and discover the endless possibilities of Wildwood.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303470/extras/Connect.gif?t=1691646336\" /><br>Connect your settlement with a logistics network of trains and wagons. Move resources to where they are needed to ensure the survival of your settlement and to keep your citizens well provided for<br><br>Wildwood provides a unique challenge for players who want a survival city builder that allows you to endlessly expand your world. Start building your settlement today!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303470/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1691646336","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303470/page_bg_generated.